<div class="banner">
  <div class="banner-line"><%= render "shared/line" %></div>
  <div class="banner-text">
    <div class="banner-text-main">
      <h1>
        Master the LSAT
        <br>
        <small>Unlock Your Future Career</small>
      </h1>
      <p>World-class instruction, taught to you in a 1-on-1 custom format</p>
      <%= link_to "Start now", new_coaching_request_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-light" %>
      <%= link_to "Know more", about_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-link text-white" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="banner-logo">
    <div class="banner-logo-main"><%= render "shared/logo" %></div>
    <div class="banner-shadow"><%= render "shared/logo" %></div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-primary p-3 text-center">
  <% Section.first(3).each do |section| %>
    <%= link_to  section.title, course_section_path(section), class: "btn btn-primary mx-1" %>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="dark-gray-wrapper padded main-content-text">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-6">
        <h2 class="text-white text-right border-top border-bottom py-3">
          About
          <br>
          LSAT Cracked
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="col-6 text-white">
        <p>I started LSAT Cracked to scale the impact of my 1-on-1 private coaching. I know 90% of the pre-law market can’t afford private sessions, and mass-market LSAT providers vary widely in quality. Even the relatively good ones are still less than completely rigorous in how they teach the underlying logic and reading skills that the LSAT demands.</p>
        <p>I love teaching. And I really love teaching students to reason logically, think critically, and read intelligently. I also love the freedom, leanness, and total responsibility that running my own business entails.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<footer class="main-content-text">
  <div class="footer-logo"><%= render "shared/logo" %></div>
  <p class="border-top mt-3 pt-3 w-100 text-center">
    © 2020 lsatcracked.com
  </p>
</footer>
